WEBVTT

00:01.500 --> 00:02.490
《越狱》前情回顾
Previously on prison break

00:03.400 --> 00:06.390
那群混蛋死了还好 我们却辛苦的活着
Those ass-hats are worth more dead than you and I are alive.

00:06.400 --> 00:08.650
有人会得到那笔钱 最好是我
Somebody's gonna get that money-- might as well be me.

00:08.660 --> 00:09.950
你知道 像那种工作
You know,a job like that

00:09.960 --> 00:14.090
有个帮手会更轻松点
might go a little smoother with an extra pair of hands.

00:14.100 --> 00:16.220
派些潜水员到河里去
I want divers down in the river.

00:16.230 --> 00:17.390
你是斯科特 科波莱内吗?
<i>Are you Scott Kolbrenner?</i>

00:17.400 --> 00:18.990
那你就是黛布拉 珍了
<i>You must be Debra Jean.</i>

00:19.000 --> 00:19.920
很高兴认识你
It's nice to meet you.

00:19.930 --> 00:20.920
我也是
Yeah,same here.

00:20.930 --> 00:22.820
很显然菲波纳奇会再次出庭
Apparently,Fibonacci's coming up for air again,

00:22.830 --> 00:25.490
如果他在那个听证会上作证
and if he testifies at that hearing,

00:25.500 --> 00:27.150
很多人都会被拖下水
a lot of people are going down.

00:27.160 --> 00:29.020
卡罗琳 他们把她带走了
Caroline. They're taking her in.

00:29.030 --> 00:30.520
当然 我会密切关注她的
Of course,I'll keep an eye on her.

00:30.530 --> 00:32.420
你好 我叫莎拉 是个瘾君子
Hi,my name is Sara,and I'm an addict.

00:32.430 --> 00:34.490
我叫兰斯 也是个瘾君子
Hi,my name's Lance,and I'm an addict.

00:34.500 --> 00:35.970
你好 兰斯
Hi,Lance.

00:37.630 --> 00:39.490
你干得真他妈的好
<i>You did one hell of a job,Doc.</i>

00:39.500 --> 00:40.820
你可以离开了
It's okay for you to leave now.

00:40.830 --> 00:43.100
我可以走 你却不行
Oh,I'm leaving; you're not.

00:44.600 --> 00:46.020
去哪里 先生
Where to,sir?

00:46.030 --> 00:47.650
犹他州
Utah.

00:47.660 --> 00:50.730
准备好了? 是
Ready? Yeah.

00:55.360 --> 00:56.720
是他们中的哪个?
<i>So which one of them was it?</i>

00:56.730 --> 00:58.090
可能是斯科菲尔德
Maybe Scofield.

00:58.100 --> 01:00.120
很可能还能找到他的哥哥
Probably gonna find his brother in there,too.

01:00.130 --> 01:03.190
你还会见她吗 那个医生
Are you meeting up with her,the doctor?

01:03.200 --> 01:04.300
我也不清楚
I don't know.

01:06.300 --> 01:08.630
我就知道这小婊子会带我们找到他们
I knew the little whore would take us right to 'em.

01:11.700 --> 01:13.990
到了墨西哥 你们打算干什么?
<i>What happens when you get to Mexico?</i>

01:14.000 --> 01:15.190
你们打算去哪?
<i>Where will you go?</i>

01:15.200 --> 01:17.650
你不知道为好
It's best if you don't know.

01:17.660 --> 01:19.220
所有人都不知道最好
It's best for everyone.

01:19.230 --> 01:21.620
下个镇子你就下车
We'll drop you off in the next town,

01:21.630 --> 01:25.350
我说过会给你寄一万美金的
and I'll wire you that 10,000,like I said.

01:25.360 --> 01:28.960
不会超过两个星期
Shouldn't take more than a week or two.

01:29.500 --> 01:32.100
迈克尔 我们有麻烦了
Michael.What's hell going on?

01:43.730 --> 01:47.600
抓紧 抓紧了
Hold on! Hold on! Hold on!

01:50.620 --> 01:53.560
是谁?
Who is it?

01:56.750 --> 01:57.710
是贝利克
It's Bellick!

02:07.400 --> 02:09.550
抓紧
Hold on.

02:09.560 --> 02:11.520
抓紧 抓紧了...
Hold on,hold on,hold on.

02:11.530 --> 02:13.900
抓紧
Hold on.

02:18.960 --> 02:20.540
这东西就不能开快一点吗
Can this thing go any faster?!

02:22.200 --> 02:25.330
你认为呢?
What do you think?!

03:01.430 --> 03:04.930
小心 小心!
Look out!

03:20.530 --> 03:23.230
都不准动
Nobody move!

03:23.300 --> 03:24.580
都不准动
Nobody move!

03:25.800 --> 03:28.190
真高兴又见到你了 孩子
Oh,good to see you again,boy.

03:29.070 --> 03:30.980
大家都不想受伤 老大
No need for anyoneto get hurt,Boss.

03:31.630 --> 03:34.850
老大?  这里再也用不着讲礼貌了
Boss? Oh,there's no need for formalities anymore there,Sink.

03:34.860 --> 03:36.720
我再也不是公务员了
I'm no longer an employee of the state,

03:36.730 --> 03:38.090
都是拜你所赐
thanks to you.

03:38.100 --> 03:40.190
我想是有人想要那笔赏金
I think somebody wants that reward.

03:40.200 --> 03:43.050
这跟赏金无关 伙计
Oh,it's not about reward money,friend.

03:43.060 --> 03:44.620
你的朋友曼彻全都告诉我了
Your pal Manche told me

03:44.630 --> 03:46.850
关于韦斯特莫兰德隐藏的
all about your little treasure hunt

03:46.860 --> 03:48.850
小小的寻宝游戏
for Westmoreland's stash.

03:49.640 --> 03:50.500
上车
Get in the car.

03:52.400 --> 03:54.890
我们要去犹他州了
We're going to Utah.

04:29.770 --> 04:32.190
这里所有的警察都在找你们
All the cops following you all over the country,

04:32.200 --> 04:34.790
但是都是追着你们的尾巴跑
when all they had to do was tail the tail,you know?

04:34.800 --> 04:37.590
走快点 我的摇钱树
Let's move it,convict.

04:37.600 --> 04:40.990
既然你们已经知道犹他的那笔钱 为什么还需要我们
If you know about the money in Utah,why do you need us?

04:41.000 --> 04:42.090
越狱太过紧张
Well,the excitement of the escape,

04:42.100 --> 04:43.590
在那老家伙挂之前
Manche didn't hear everything Westmoreland said

04:43.600 --> 04:45.590
曼彻没把韦斯特莫兰德的话都听完
before the old bird kicked the bucket,

04:45.600 --> 04:47.960
但是他听清楚了 犹他和五百万
but he heard enough: Utah and five million.

04:47.970 --> 04:49.940
加上你们就够了
You'll fill in the blanks.

04:51.070 --> 04:53.130
别在这里装腔作势 傻瓜
Don't even think about getting cute,smart-ass.

04:53.140 --> 04:54.760
现在你和你哥哥带我们
Now,you and your brother are gonna take me

04:54.770 --> 04:56.090
去找那笔钱
right to where that money is,

04:56.100 --> 04:59.100
否则这婊子就死得很快
or the whore gets dead real fast.

04:59.170 --> 05:01.150
不信就试试看
Ask me if I'm bluffing.

05:13.720 --> 05:15.740
从斯科菲尔德公寓底下那条河里
The dredging of the river beneath Scofield's apartment

05:15.750 --> 05:16.890
找到一些东西
bore some fruit.

05:18.170 --> 05:20.490
河床底找到一个硬盘
Found a hard drive under the river bed.

05:20.500 --> 05:21.530
上面的序列号
Serial numbers match an order

05:21.540 --> 05:23.130
跟他进监狱前几个月
that Scofield put in with Dell

05:23.140 --> 05:24.530
购买的戴尔电脑相吻合
a few months before he was incarcerated.

05:24.540 --> 05:29.340
现在他们恢复了上面12%的数据
They've recovered about 12 percent of the data so far.

05:47.270 --> 05:49.190
这个对我们有什么帮助
And this is helping us how?

05:49.200 --> 05:50.330
血液检验已经出来了
Blood tests came back.

05:50.340 --> 05:52.760
爆炸地点都是B型
B-negative all over that crash site.

05:52.770 --> 05:54.390
斯科菲尔德和布伦斯也都是...
Scofield and Burrows are both...

05:54.400 --> 05:55.790
B型 -我知道
B-negative. -I know.

05:55.800 --> 05:57.260
我去联系媒体
I'll reach out to the media.

05:57.270 --> 05:59.260
别忙这么做
How about don't.

05:59.270 --> 06:02.570
如果我们对外宣称策划越狱的
If it gets out that the guy who...

06:02.870 --> 06:06.230
主犯可能已经死了
...who masterminded this whole thing is possibly dead,

06:06.240 --> 06:08.230
其他六个家伙就会更加警觉
the other six cons are gonna get their guards up even more.

06:08.240 --> 06:10.060
我们的策略是 抱歉...
It is our policy-- excuse me...

06:10.070 --> 06:11.430
我们的策略是
It is our policy

06:11.440 --> 06:13.960
在确认他们死亡之前先别声张
<i>not</i> to announce deaths until they're confirmed!

06:16.040 --> 06:18.290
我们已经看到汽车爆炸和血液检测
We've got an exploding car and a blood match.

06:18.300 --> 06:19.390
那就做更多检验
Well,then do more tests.

06:19.400 --> 06:20.660
对什么做检验?
On what?

06:20.670 --> 06:22.360
对汽车保险杆 我不知道 也不在乎
On the bumper. I don't know. I don't care.

06:22.370 --> 06:24.660
先别忙 我想让外面的那些家伙
Just delay. I want those guys out there

06:24.670 --> 06:26.290
更得意 而不是更小心
getting more complacent,not more careful.

06:30.240 --> 06:32.560
继续向他们的核计划迈进
<i>...to forge ahead with its nuclear program.</i>

06:32.570 --> 06:35.060
国内新闻 从福克斯河监狱
In national news,the eight escaped convicts

06:35.070 --> 06:37.130
越狱的8名逃犯
from Fox River Penitentiary in Illinois

06:37.140 --> 06:39.730
目前仍在逃中...
are still at large,and...

06:39.740 --> 06:42.430
我正在听呢
Hey,I was listening to that.

06:42.440 --> 06:43.460
是啊
Yeah.

06:43.470 --> 06:45.230
但是我想听这个
Yeah,I want to hear this.

06:45.240 --> 06:46.230
真的吗
Really?

06:46.240 --> 06:47.720
你喜欢约翰·丹佛?
You like John Denver?

06:49.290 --> 06:50.230
当然
Yeah.

06:59.970 --> 07:01.890
带我回家
Take me home

07:01.900 --> 07:05.960
到你的家
To your place

07:05.970 --> 07:09.090
我有现钞...
I've got cash

07:11.500 --> 07:13.660
西弗吉尼亚
In West Virginia

07:13.670 --> 07:19.060
带我回家 我的乡村妓女
Take me home,my country ho...

07:19.070 --> 07:20.230
不错 很不错
This is good,this is good.

07:20.240 --> 07:21.860
歌唱的不错 都可以弃学专业当歌手了
Don't quit your day job.

07:21.870 --> 07:24.130
什么
What?

07:24.140 --> 07:27.690
通常我是喝点龙舌兰酒才开始K歌
Nah,I just need a little tequila to get my karaoke on.

07:27.700 --> 07:30.940
不错
<i>Yeah.</i>

07:32.200 --> 07:35.400
慢着 减速
Here,yo,slow down.

07:36.540 --> 07:38.030
我们现在只有65码 限速60...
We're doing,like,65 in a 60...

07:38.040 --> 07:39.730
减速
Yo,slow down.

07:39.740 --> 07:42.740
好吧 老兄
All right,Dad.

07:46.970 --> 07:49.130
我们不能被查到 伙计
Yo,we can't be having that,man.

07:49.140 --> 07:51.690
开张罚单就是200美刀
Tickets are,like,200 bones.

07:51.700 --> 07:55.270
是啊
Yeah.

07:56.170 --> 07:58.730
我从没想过要说这句话 斯科菲尔德
I never thought I'd say this,Scofield,

07:58.740 --> 08:01.390
我真的感谢上帝让你来到福克斯河
but I thank God for the day you walked into Fox River.

08:01.400 --> 08:03.060
然后又逃了出去
And out of it.

08:04.870 --> 08:06.260
没事的
It's gonna be okay.

08:07.760 --> 08:09.620
我可不想听你说这句话
I don't want to hear from you right now.

08:10.230 --> 08:11.380
你告诉我什么都不会发生
You told me nothing would happen.

08:12.300 --> 08:13.410
你向我保证了
You promised me.

08:17.140 --> 08:18.580
她生气了
That's one pissed off commie

08:18.580 --> 08:20.530
你可得自己解决 斯科菲尔德
you got on your hands there,Scofield.

08:21.290 --> 08:22.960
你妈妈没告诉你怎么对待一个女人吗?
Didn't your mama tell you how to treat a lady?

08:23.540 --> 08:25.700
还是她自己就是这样的一个婊子 林肯
Or was she a whore like this one? Linc!

08:26.210 --> 08:27.460
有问题吗 布伦斯
Got a problem there,Burrows?

08:28.060 --> 08:29.170
我们只需要你们中的一个
We only need one of you

08:29.180 --> 08:30.430
带我们去找那笔钱
to take us to the money.

08:30.900 --> 08:31.940
记好了
Remember that.

08:34.120 --> 08:34.890
我们走 伙计
Let's go,buddy.

08:35.240 --> 08:37.190
走吧
Let's go.

08:37.600 --> 08:40.390
在说结婚祝词的时候 我完全喝醉了
I'd been really drunk at the wedding speech.

08:40.400 --> 08:41.890
这是我第一次
And this was the first time

08:41.900 --> 08:44.050
在这里跟大家说
that we'd spoken since then.

08:45.440 --> 08:46.340
让我得到净化
And it was cleansing.

08:46.350 --> 08:47.640
真的让我得到净化
It was really cleansing.

08:48.970 --> 08:49.620
谢谢
Thank you.

08:54.140 --> 08:55.570
谢谢你的参与 拉尔夫
Good share,Ralph.

08:56.090 --> 08:57.050
我们没多少时间了
Well,we're out of time.

08:57.450 --> 08:59.250
除非还有特别想说的
Unless there are any burning desires...

08:59.250 --> 09:00.270
我想谈一下
Actually,I'd like to...

09:01.490 --> 09:02.690
如果有时间允许的话
you know,if there's time.

09:03.260 --> 09:03.990
当然
Of course.

09:06.660 --> 09:08.010
我叫兰斯 我是个瘾君子
I'm Lance,and I'm an addict.

09:09.270 --> 09:10.030
你好 兰斯
Hi,Lance.

09:12.000 --> 09:16.050
上周我妈妈死于多发性硬化症
My,uh,mother died of M.S. last week.

09:17.610 --> 09:18.500
她是...
She just...

09:19.640 --> 09:21.760
一点点耗光的
gave out.

09:21.770 --> 09:24.660
就像我的外祖父 我的姐姐一样
Just like my grandfather did,just like my sister did.

09:24.670 --> 09:27.160
如果任其发展下去  我也一样
Just like I...

09:27.170 --> 09:30.560
可以打断一下吗
Um,if-if I may?

09:30.570 --> 09:34.360
兰斯  多发性硬化症通常不遗传
Lance,M.S. isn't usually considered genetic.

09:34.370 --> 09:36.130
是吗 什么 你是医生吗?
Really? What-What are you,a doctor?

09:38.170 --> 09:40.770
我是 事实上
Uh,I-I am,actually.

09:43.800 --> 09:44.510
抱歉
Sorry.

09:47.040 --> 09:48.850
谢谢大家
Thank you.

09:59.770 --> 10:02.060
好了 大家都面对墙
All right,everybody,face the wall

10:02.070 --> 10:03.340
看着前方
and look straight ahead!

10:08.040 --> 10:09.440
眼睛看前面
Eyes front.

10:09.700 --> 10:11.260
旅途怎么样啊？
How was your flight?

10:11.270 --> 10:12.830
一路颠簸
Bumpy.

10:12.840 --> 10:13.890
一切都准备好了吧?
Everything is ready?

10:13.900 --> 10:15.660
我们有艘货船泊在军港里
We got a container ship down at the navy yard.

10:15.670 --> 10:17.160
船长是我们的人
The captain's one of ours.

10:17.170 --> 10:19.090
船上有个贵宾间
He's got a stateroom

10:19.100 --> 10:20.130
旅客清单上标记此房间装货用
listed as a cargo hold on the manifest.

10:20.140 --> 10:21.490
你和你家人上这条船
You and your family will be on it

10:21.500 --> 10:22.990
明天就起航
when it sets sail tomorrow.

10:23.000 --> 10:26.510
六天后 约翰 你就会在撒丁岛了
Six days from now,John,you'll be in Sardinia.

10:26.530 --> 10:27.690
干的好
Good work.

10:35.040 --> 10:35.870
西尔维娅
Sylvia.

10:35.870 --> 10:37.330
爸爸!
Dad!

10:42.900 --> 10:43.740
我们想你
We missed you.

10:45.310 --> 10:46.690
结束了
It's over.

10:49.880 --> 10:51.010
我也想你们
I missed you,too.

10:58.300 --> 11:00.530
好了 都结束了
It's over,it's over.

11:41.900 --> 11:44.970
来吧
Come on.

11:52.940 --> 11:57.330
来吧
Come on.

11:57.340 --> 12:00.500
你在搞什么鬼
What the hell are you doing?

12:04.340 --> 12:05.560
管好你自己的事吧
Mind your own business.

12:18.540 --> 12:20.460
你这没用的东西
What kind of son of a bitch

12:20.470 --> 12:22.090
居然在车里不放备用胎?
doesn't have a spare tire in his car?

12:22.100 --> 12:23.960
你不是还用得着我
The kind that already used it.

12:23.970 --> 12:25.490
你真是个没用的家伙
Well,then you're just the sad sack

12:25.500 --> 12:28.130
得回城里去弄个新的了
that has to go back into town to get a new one.

12:28.140 --> 12:29.490
有将近三里啊
That's like three miles.

12:29.500 --> 12:30.770
是的
That's right.

12:34.180 --> 12:35.160
好了 大家都出来
All right,everybody out.

12:42.190 --> 12:43.370
那边 走吧
That way,come on.

12:49.300 --> 12:50.960
小心点
Careful.

12:50.970 --> 12:53.390
别碰我
Don't touch me.

12:53.400 --> 12:54.830
放轻松点
Just relax.

12:54.840 --> 12:57.090
我信你说的每句话
You know,I believed everything you told me,

12:57.100 --> 12:59.230
我做了你让我做的每件事
and I did everything you asked.

12:59.240 --> 13:01.130
我为了你不惜冒生命危险
I risked my life for you.

13:01.140 --> 13:03.390
为了什么?就为了那1万美元吗？ 我在冒生命的危险啊！
For what? For $10,000,I risked my life?

13:03.400 --> 13:05.030
而与此同时
And this entire time,

13:05.040 --> 13:08.490
有500万美元在那里等你
you've had $5 million just waiting there.

13:08.500 --> 13:10.670
你是个混蛋 迈克尔
You're a bastard,Michael.

13:12.040 --> 13:14.790
不好受吧 我倒希望这样的事
For all the aggravation,I hope you got to hit that

13:14.800 --> 13:15.810
你多碰到几次 斯科菲尔德
a few times,Scofield.

13:18.200 --> 13:20.130
呵呵呵
Ba-ba-boom-bah.

13:20.140 --> 13:22.330
我们去棚房那里等吧
We're going to wait it out in that shack.

13:25.170 --> 13:26.360
进去 动作麻利点
Go in there.Come on.

13:32.900 --> 13:34.040
小宝贝 别停下
Fantasia,get going.

13:35.800 --> 13:38.560
我想和你谈谈... 单独
I need to talk to you... alone.

13:38.570 --> 13:40.490
你要怎样？
What do you want?

13:40.500 --> 13:42.730
毁了他的生活就像他曾经毁了我的那样
To ruin his life like he's ruined mine.

13:51.760 --> 13:53.520
你看见了什么，先生？
And what did you see, sir?

13:53.560 --> 13:54.490
我车子过热了
I was overheating,

13:54.490 --> 13:55.280
所以我停车了
so I pulled in.

13:55.320 --> 13:56.720
这车已经在这了
This car was already here.

13:56.760 --> 13:58.240
你呢？
What about you?

13:58.280 --> 13:59.070
我在看书
Oh, I was reading;

13:59.070 --> 14:00.000
我什么也没看见
I didn't see nothing.

14:00.040 --> 14:01.760
嘿，伙计
Hey, buddy.

14:01.800 --> 14:03.790
你从哪来的?
Where you coming from?

14:03.800 --> 14:05.090
我?
Me?

14:05.100 --> 14:07.760
我刚刚撞了下头 长官
I was just hitting the head,boss.

14:07.770 --> 14:11.000
你叫什么名字?
What's your name?

14:11.300 --> 14:13.490
克莱德
Clyde.

14:13.500 --> 14:14.920
克莱德 梅
Clyde May.

14:14.930 --> 14:17.060
有身份证件吗 梅先生?
You got any ID,Mr. May?

14:17.070 --> 14:18.590
我不能...
I don't,uh...

14:18.600 --> 14:22.590
我不能再开车了 所以证件不随身带
drive anymore,so don't really have ID per se.

14:22.600 --> 14:25.060
在坎大哈的时候 有帮阿拉伯兔崽子
Camel jockey left a big box of boom-boom

14:25.070 --> 14:27.830
在我吉普车下面埋了雷...
under my jeep back in Kandahar.

14:28.750 --> 14:29.400
你是军人?
You military?

14:30.550 --> 14:31.390
过去是
Was.

14:31.960 --> 14:32.940
哪辆车是你的?
Which one's your vehicle?

14:33.630 --> 14:35.330
就这两条腿
These two sleds right here.

14:36.190 --> 14:38.350
也就是，总之就靠这移动了
That is,in between rides,anyhow.

14:38.960 --> 14:40.580
怎么没带行李啊？
Ain't much of a bag to be hitchhiking with.

14:42.190 --> 14:43.190
我喜欢轻装上路啊
I travel light.

14:43.760 --> 14:46.550
你就这样凭空走到这里的？
And you're just hoofing it out here in the middle of nowhere?

14:46.550 --> 14:48.700
我总有权利四处看看这个国家
I do have the right to see a little bit of the country

14:48.700 --> 14:49.880
这个我为之断手的国家吧?
I lost my hand for,don't I?

14:51.100 --> 14:52.810
告诉我究竟怎么了 长官？
Why don't you tell me what this is all about,Officer.

14:52.810 --> 14:54.800
我们找到了辆车 但是没有司机
We got a vehicle here without a driver,

14:55.430 --> 14:56.150
现在呢
and at present,

14:56.150 --> 14:58.010
你是这里唯一一个没车的司机
you're the only driver without a vehicle.

14:59.080 --> 15:00.580
嘿 就是为了这件事啊?
Hell,is that what this is all about?

15:01.150 --> 15:02.350
为什么不早说啊?
Why didn't you say so?

15:04.420 --> 15:07.120
有个脏兮兮的嬉皮士刚才跑进去拉屎
Dirty hippie kid dropping a deuce in the facilities.

15:07.130 --> 15:08.220
就是开着这辆车来的
Came in with that car

15:08.230 --> 15:09.220
不到两分钟前
not two minutes ago.

15:10.580 --> 15:11.110
去查查
Check it out.

15:21.260 --> 15:22.300
你以前是陆军部队的？
What were you,Army?

15:23.020 --> 15:23.720
当然不是
Hell no.

15:24.670 --> 15:25.460
海军陆战队
Corps.

15:25.900 --> 15:26.810
哦 是这样啊
Well,then.

15:26.810 --> 15:28.150
永远效忠（注:海军陆战队的宣言）
Semper fi,brother.

15:28.870 --> 15:29.720
哪个番号的？
What outfit were you?

15:31.350 --> 15:33.080
第196师
196th.

15:34.710 --> 15:36.230
第196师?
196th?

15:38.400 --> 15:39.250
从没听说过啊
Never heard of it.

15:40.360 --> 15:41.100
在哪的?
Where they out of?

15:42.280 --> 15:43.210
嘿!
Hey,Elkind!

15:44.310 --> 15:45.010
这他妈怎么回事?
What the hell,man?

15:45.010 --> 15:45.770
我什么都没做
I didn't do nothing.

15:47.420 --> 15:48.700
在他背包里发现了这些
Found these in his knapsack,

15:49.080 --> 15:50.490
在他告诉我他没车后
after he said he had no car.

15:51.180 --> 15:51.850
什么?
What?

15:58.020 --> 15:59.170
永远效忠
Semper fi,brother.

16:01.010 --> 16:02.030
永远效忠
Semper fi.

16:07.700 --> 16:09.770
不用使劲了 没什么用的
Stop stressing; it doesn't do any good.

16:11.400 --> 16:13.170
或许你应该开始使劲
Maybe you ought to  <i>start</i> stressing,

16:13.190 --> 16:14.850
如果他们准备一枪毙了你
if they're going to put a bullet in our heads.

16:15.790 --> 16:16.580
他们需要我们
They need us.

16:17.620 --> 16:19.030
他们需要我们帮他们拿到钱
They need us to get that money.

16:19.030 --> 16:20.610
我真佩服你的乐观精神
I admire your optimism.

16:22.020 --> 16:23.020
她的立场不定
She's rolling,man.

16:23.880 --> 16:24.640
我能感觉到
I can feel it.

16:25.750 --> 16:27.580
你想要毁了斯科菲尔德的一生
<i>So you want to ruin</i>  <i>Scofield's life.</i>

16:27.580 --> 16:28.610
欢迎加入
Well,get in line.

16:30.600 --> 16:31.770
你到底想要什么?
What are you really looking for?

16:32.730 --> 16:35.080
和你一样 钱！
Same as you... money.

16:36.100 --> 16:37.310
钱? 你想要钱?
Money? You want money?

16:37.310 --> 16:39.600
一万美元 怎么样?
Ten grand,how's that sound?

16:40.110 --> 16:42.830
我们现在就干 在那地板上
We do it right now,right there on those floorboards.

16:43.580 --> 16:45.320
想都别想
Not in a thousand years.

16:45.950 --> 16:46.940
那就给我滚
Beat it then.

16:47.340 --> 16:48.480
你身上没有其他我要的东西
You got nothing else I need.

16:48.490 --> 16:49.590
男的都这样啊
Typical man.

16:50.480 --> 16:51.860
我说的是数百万的美元
I'm talking about millions of dollars,

16:51.870 --> 16:53.450
你他妈就为了做爱连钱都不要了
and you'd piss it away for sex.

16:53.460 --> 16:54.580
是的
That's right.

16:55.190 --> 16:57.680
我之前还希望你不要让斯科菲尔德赢了你
And I was hoping you wouldn't let Michael outsmart you,too.

16:58.630 --> 17:01.010
斯科菲尔德 没赢任何人
Scofield ain't outsmarting no one.

17:01.570 --> 17:03.560
你以为那胎是偶然爆掉的啊?
You think that tire went flat by accident?

17:06.350 --> 17:07.350
你有什么要告诉我?
What are you offering?

17:07.360 --> 17:09.460
我能找到钱在哪
I can find out where the money is.

17:09.470 --> 17:10.290
他信我
He trusts me.

17:10.780 --> 17:11.490
你想要什么?
What do you want?

17:11.930 --> 17:12.880
我应得的那份
My fair share.

17:13.540 --> 17:15.720
你找到钱在哪 你就可以得到
You find out where that money is,your fair share

17:16.100 --> 17:17.410
20万美元
is $200,000.

17:17.420 --> 17:19.270
5百万只分这点? 这不公平...
Out of five million? It's not even...

17:19.270 --> 17:20.650
我拿着枪呢 小妞
I got the gun,girl.

17:21.270 --> 17:22.820
我让你加入 你该感到庆幸了
You're lucky you're a partner at all.

17:27.030 --> 17:28.090
我马上就回来
I'll be right back

17:32.630 --> 17:34.920
菲波纳奇在华盛顿
Fibonacci's in D.C.

17:34.930 --> 17:37.390
是的 他还在丹佛 亚特兰大 迈阿密...
Yeah,and he's in Denver,Atlanta,Miami...

17:37.400 --> 17:38.560
不不不不
No,no,no,no,no.

17:38.570 --> 17:40.320
这次是真的
This time,it's for real.

17:40.330 --> 17:41.760
他又要作证了
He's testifying again.

17:41.770 --> 17:43.590
他现在在华盛顿
He's in Washington right now.

17:43.600 --> 17:45.920
环球旅馆116房间
The Globe Hotel,Room 116.

17:45.930 --> 17:47.820
这个消息可靠吗?
Is this information any good?

17:47.830 --> 17:49.720
是从新泽西来的
It's from New Jersey.

17:49.730 --> 17:52.010
费希赫德 汤米想示好
Fishhead Tommy wants to pay tribute.

17:55.400 --> 17:56.160
去准备车
Get the car.

17:56.170 --> 17:57.060
好的
Okay.

18:02.870 --> 18:05.290
看看这里 约翰
Look at this room,John.

18:06.870 --> 18:07.620
看看
Look.

18:10.070 --> 18:12.260
我们又可以成为一家人了
We can be a family again.

18:13.090 --> 18:14.240
但是你又要去拿这一切冒险了
But you want to risk it all,

18:14.240 --> 18:16.430
你不重视我们 为了什么 为了报仇吗?
disrespect us,and for what,for vengeance?

18:17.610 --> 18:18.330
他背叛了我
He betrayed me.

18:18.330 --> 18:19.850
我不管
I don't care.

18:19.850 --> 18:21.020
他背叛了我们
He betrayed us.

18:22.660 --> 18:26.190
对不起 你... 你永远不会明白
I'm sorry you... will never understand

18:27.660 --> 18:31.980
在监狱的时候... 到底发生了什么？
what happens... when you're in prison.

18:32.800 --> 18:34.710
你又会被关进去的...
But you could go back to pris...

18:36.080 --> 18:36.910
我向天发誓...
I swear to God...

18:39.320 --> 18:42.390
我宁愿死也不会回去
I'd rather die than go back.

18:42.390 --> 18:45.340
没有回头路了 没了 再也没了
There's no going back,never,ever again.

18:46.880 --> 18:50.460
约翰 耶稣拯救了你 不要违背他的意愿
Christ saved you,John.Don't turn your back on him.

18:51.780 --> 18:54.050
不要不顾我们
Don't turn your back on us.

19:03.640 --> 19:04.970
我...
I...

19:16.550 --> 19:18.950
我不知道 大约离冈尼森河20里
I don't know,about 20 miles from Gunnison.

19:19.950 --> 19:21.340
他来了  我得挂了
He's coming; I have to go.

19:25.910 --> 19:26.570
是谁啊?
Who was that?

19:27.440 --> 19:28.730
不是别人 是我爸爸
Nobody,it's just my father.

19:28.730 --> 19:29.810
哦 嘿 听着
Oh. Hey,listen.

19:30.610 --> 19:32.300
我们在下个汽车旅店打尖行吗?
Do you mind if we stop at the next motel?

19:34.050 --> 19:35.170
还只有大约四点啊?
It's only like 4:00?

19:35.180 --> 19:36.580
是的 但是我们已经开了很久
Yeah,but we've been driving forever.

19:37.700 --> 19:38.510
好吧 我来开
It's cool,I'll drive.

19:39.570 --> 19:40.740
我真的想停一停
I really just want to stop.

19:41.990 --> 19:43.160
但是如果我们现在上路的话 或许...
But if we get on the road now,maybe...

19:43.160 --> 19:44.860
斯科特 这是我的车
Scott,it's my car,

19:44.860 --> 19:47.160
我很累了 好吗?
and I'm tired of being in it,okay?

19:48.810 --> 19:49.580
好吧
All right.

19:54.970 --> 19:56.220
-听过那个暴料的来电吗? -你能相信吗?
<i>Can you believe it?</i>

19:56.220 --> 19:58.780
全靠这个小人物菲波纳奇
Of all the players in this thing,

19:58.810 --> 20:00.570
给了我们提示 快点
it's the rat that could give us our first collar. Come on.

20:03.050 --> 20:05.040
你们俩想上厕所 都给我摒住
You guys need to use the can,hold it.

20:05.830 --> 20:07.070
小宝贝 如果你想小便
If you need to tinkle,sweet pea,

20:07.070 --> 20:09.370
我随时可以照看你
I'll watch you any time.

20:10.380 --> 20:11.190
坐下
Sit down.

20:13.650 --> 20:14.670
把手放后面
Hands behind your back.

20:29.750 --> 20:30.460
慢慢来
Took your time.

20:32.730 --> 20:34.920
要获得一个男人的信任得花点时间
It takes time to gain a man's confidence.

20:36.690 --> 20:37.580
你说的没错
You're right.

20:37.580 --> 20:39.260
他会怀疑我说的任何事的
He'll bite on anything I say.

20:40.090 --> 20:41.380
你告诉我我们在哪设计抓他
You just tell me where we trap him,

20:41.380 --> 20:43.720
然后我就告诉他钱在哪
and I'll tell him that's where the money is.

21:03.570 --> 21:06.150
嘿 你就是刚才加油站的那个人 是吗?
Hey,you're the guy from the gas station,right?

21:06.150 --> 21:07.140
是的
Yeah.

21:07.140 --> 21:08.620
刚才我的车出了点问题
I'm the guy who was having car trouble.

21:12.320 --> 21:13.810
现在听起来有点咕噜咕噜响?
Seems to be purring along now,huh?

21:14.570 --> 21:16.850
是的 是抽水机的问题
Yeah. Water pump.

21:18.310 --> 21:19.910
这辆破车花了200美金
200 bucks for this heap.

21:21.480 --> 21:23.210
它们会让你烦躁不安
Well,they'll get you.

21:23.210 --> 21:25.240
希望我没有多管闲事
Look,I-I hope I'm not out of line,

21:25.240 --> 21:28.220
不过刚才我在那里听到你和警察 说起有关你手的事情
but I heard you telling the cop back there about your hand.

21:28.230 --> 21:30.660
当我还是个孩子的时候 我老父就在越南遇害了
My old man was killed in 'Nam when I was a kid,

21:30.660 --> 21:33.470
所以我对军人非常尊敬
and so I have the utmost respect for our servicemen.

21:33.470 --> 21:35.080
仅仅是为国效劳罢了
Just serving my country.

21:35.900 --> 21:37.140
我们许多人都为此表示感激
A lot of us are grateful for it.

21:38.070 --> 21:39.640
如果你需要搭个顺风车什么的...
Listen,if you need a ride or something...

21:41.410 --> 21:43.350
坦白和你说 我的...
Well,to be honest with you,my...

21:44.440 --> 21:46.080
我的脚走的好酸
my dogs are kind of barking.

21:46.960 --> 21:47.940
好的 上车吧
Well,all right.

21:48.870 --> 21:49.550
我是杰瑞 柯顿
Jerry Curtin.

21:51.280 --> 21:54.110
克莱德  克莱德 梅
Clyde. Clyde May.

21:55.760 --> 21:56.520
我女儿丹尼儿坐在前座
My kid Danny's riding shotgun.

21:56.520 --> 21:57.340
我想你不介意
I hope you don't mind

21:57.340 --> 21:58.440
坐在后面
sittingin the back.

22:00.660 --> 22:01.630
嗨 我是丹尼儿
Hi. I'm Danielle.

22:05.340 --> 22:06.460
嗨 你好
Hi,yourself.

22:16.530 --> 22:19.790
-嘿 -你想干吗?
<i>Hey.</i>What do you want?

22:19.800 --> 22:22.060
我要上洗手间
I need to use the bathroom.

22:22.070 --> 22:23.260
又要去?
Again?

22:23.270 --> 22:25.020
我膀胱小
I have a small bladder.

22:25.030 --> 22:27.040
你们不会都这样吧
That ain't all you got.

22:32.670 --> 22:34.550
起来
Get up.

22:43.530 --> 22:44.920
怎么样?
Well?

22:44.930 --> 22:46.220
他们计划设陷抓你
They plan to trap you.

22:46.230 --> 22:49.020
那个大个子  他在犹他有些朋友
The big one-- he's got friends in Utah.

22:49.030 --> 22:50.290
都是罪犯
Criminals.

22:50.300 --> 22:52.360
一个叫潘圭里奇的小镇
A town called Panguitch.

22:52.370 --> 22:54.390
他们在那里的农场种大麻
They grow drugs on the farm there.

22:54.400 --> 22:57.290
还会告诉你钱在那里 但实际上没有
They'll tell you that's where the money is,but no money.

22:57.300 --> 23:00.960
只有拿着枪的老朋友 在那恭候你大驾
Just old friends with guns,waiting for you.

23:00.970 --> 23:02.760
那很简单
Easy enough.

23:02.770 --> 23:05.280
我们借道潘圭里奇
We take a pass on Panguitch.

23:08.780 --> 23:10.030
钱到底在哪?
Where's the money really?

23:10.400 --> 23:13.060
我会尽快找出来
I'll find out soon enough.

23:13.070 --> 23:16.760
不过现在20万美金是旧行情了
But $200,000 was old price for this information.

23:16.770 --> 23:19.120
我要个新价钱
I want a new price.

23:19.130 --> 23:21.390
你又在和我讨价还价
She's trying to renegotiate.

23:21.400 --> 23:23.090
如果不是我
If it wasn't for me,

23:23.100 --> 23:25.460
你就会倒毙在大麻地里
you'd be face down in a marijuana farm.

23:27.210 --> 23:28.220
三分之一
One third.

23:30.100 --> 23:32.260
那消息可不值这个价
Ha!It's gonna take a lot more than information

23:32.270 --> 23:34.760
如果你想分到三分之一 小宝贝
if you want a million-six,sweet pea.

23:34.770 --> 23:36.260
要做什么?
Such as?

23:36.270 --> 23:38.220
你知道的
You know.

23:38.230 --> 23:41.490
我一直都想要的那个
Piece of that can anytime I want it.

23:41.500 --> 23:42.820
就是那个?
Is that it?

23:42.830 --> 23:44.560
你不打算打我一巴掌吗?
Aren't you gonna slap me?

23:44.570 --> 23:47.660
我和很多男人都睡过觉  相信我
I've slept with men for a lot less,trust me.

23:47.670 --> 23:50.320
那么你说过的"想都别想"如何解释呢?
And what happened to "never in a 1,000 years?"

23:50.330 --> 23:52.310
那是谈判
That was negotiating.

23:57.710 --> 23:58.830
那么
So.

24:00.860 --> 24:01.630
成交了?
Deal?

24:04.120 --> 24:05.070
成交
Deal.

24:13.750 --> 24:16.010
我找到15万美金的现金 约翰
<i>We got a $150,000 here,John.</i>

24:16.020 --> 24:17.640
就在维托利奥在索拉纳斯的住处找到的
With Vittorio's place in Solanas,

24:17.650 --> 24:19.780
我们靠这些利息都能过活了
we'll be able to live off the interest.

24:22.090 --> 24:22.960
你们的父亲呢?
Where's your father?

24:31.440 --> 24:32.350
都好了吗 老大?
<i>Everything all right,boss?</i>

24:33.460 --> 24:34.160
是的
Yeah.

24:35.450 --> 24:36.610
让我们把这档事了结了...
Let's get this over with...

24:38.580 --> 24:40.500
这样我就能回到家人身边了
so I can get back to my family.

24:42.340 --> 24:43.600
她能搞定的
She'll get it done.

24:44.780 --> 24:46.570
妮卡和我共同经历了很多
Nika and I have come too far together.

24:46.580 --> 24:48.870
当钱就在眼前 你就不能相信任何人
When money's on the line,you trust no one.

24:48.880 --> 24:49.910
有时候你必须相信
Sometimes you have to.

24:49.920 --> 24:52.410
如果你想活命 你就不能
Not if you want to survive,you don't.

24:52.420 --> 24:54.870
你真的谁也不相信 是吗?
You really don't trust anyone,do you?

24:54.880 --> 24:58.610
在发生那么多事后 你还来责问我?
Can you blame me after all that's happened?

24:58.620 --> 25:00.180
不 我是说在那之前
No,I mean before that.

25:01.480 --> 25:02.740
进监狱之前
Before prison.

25:02.750 --> 25:05.070
每当我相信某人  我都会受伤
Every time I trusted someone,I got burned.

25:05.080 --> 25:07.120
