至少让我们把你送到镇上吧
<i>At least let us take you into town.</i>

39:06.630 --> 39:07.500
不用了
No.

39:08.040 --> 39:08.940
如果我被发现和你在一起
If I'm seen with you,

39:08.940 --> 39:10.510
那就麻烦大了
it's a lot of trouble for me.

39:11.460 --> 39:12.900
我能步行过去 只有一里路而已
I can walk; it's only a mile.

39:13.630 --> 39:15.120
没有你的帮助 我们到不了现在这步
We never would've made it this far without you.

39:16.510 --> 39:18.490
但是你会丢下我
But now you're crossing the border...

39:19.080 --> 39:19.830
穿过边境...
without me.

39:20.610 --> 39:22.210
你不能和我们一起去那儿
You can't go where we're going.

39:23.180 --> 39:24.420
因为那不是你的人生
It's not a life for you.

39:28.860 --> 39:30.130
如果说那就是我的人生呢
Then that's it then.

39:31.970 --> 39:32.930
好吧  一切都结束了
It's over for good.

39:35.260 --> 39:35.830
谢谢
Thank you.

39:38.190 --> 39:38.880
注意安全
Be safe.

39:46.500 --> 39:47.160
好运
Good luck.

39:55.130 --> 39:56.220
我爱过你 迈克尔
I loved you,Michael.

39:57.910 --> 39:59.800
我想我应该放弃这段感情
And I thought I was going to get that back,

39:59.810 --> 40:01.240
你仅仅是利用我而已
but you just used me.

40:01.240 --> 40:02.200
不是那样的
That's not true.

40:02.200 --> 40:04.230
我应该比这得到的更多
I deserve more than this.

40:04.750 --> 40:06.320
绝对不止仅当个
I deserve more than just being the girl

40:06.320 --> 40:08.210
你需要帮忙 就一个电话过来的女子
that you call when you need something.

40:08.720 --> 40:10.390
你真的认为你能在犹他州找到那笔钱?
You really think you're gonna find the money in Utah?

40:10.390 --> 40:12.400
我根本不在乎埋在犹他州的钱!
I don't care about the money in Utah!

40:14.240 --> 40:15.810
我不想再犯罪了
I don't want any more crime.

40:17.020 --> 40:19.870
我把你们抓起来 我就能得到20万
I turn you in,I get $200,000.

40:20.400 --> 40:21.160
合法的钱
Legal money.

40:27.890 --> 40:29.450
现在就把你们交给警方
You're the policemen's problem now.

40:29.790 --> 40:32.900
-妮卡... -别再靠过来 不然我就开枪了!
Nika... Don't come any closer or I'll shoot you!

40:34.280 --> 40:34.950
不 你开不了枪
No,you won't.

41:05.310 --> 41:06.200
祝你好运
Good luck to you.

41:35.100 --> 41:36.090
呃 总部来电
Um,HQ called.

41:36.100 --> 41:38.470
询问你为什么不在阿布鲁奇
They're asking why you didn't intercept Abruzzi

41:38.470 --> 41:40.110
走向汽车旅馆的时候就中途截住他
when he was walking towards the motel.

41:41.220 --> 41:42.520
这家伙是黑帮老大
The man was a mob boss.

41:42.530 --> 41:44.060
正确的行动就是困住他
The right move was to get him trapped.

41:44.630 --> 41:46.030
他们说你这么做
They're saying the way you played it,

41:46.030 --> 41:47.860
结果只有一个
there was only one possible outcome.

41:47.870 --> 41:49.430
总部对我的行动有异议的话
HQ has a problem with the way I do things,

41:49.430 --> 41:50.060
那下次让他们也拿起枪
they can pick up a gun

41:50.060 --> 41:51.730
跟着我到现场处理
and follow me into the field next time.

41:59.480 --> 42:02.240
斯科菲尔德一直知道菲波纳奇是吊住阿布鲁奇的关键
Scofield always knew the rat was the key to Abruzzi.

42:03.180 --> 42:05.610
我们偏偏把这个诱饵公布出来 这样阿布鲁奇就会上钩了
We just put it out on the wire and Abruzzi bit.

42:15.310 --> 42:16.420
说到斯科菲尔德...
Speaking of Scofield...

42:17.470 --> 42:18.620
撞车是设计好的障眼法
That crash was staged.

42:26.450 --> 42:27.110
是猪血
Pig blood.

42:30.060 --> 42:30.850
真狡猾啊
Smart kid.

42:37.100 --> 42:38.310
问题是...
The problem with...

42:40.030 --> 42:41.740
太过狡猾迟早会
being that clever is that sooner or later,

42:41.740 --> 42:43.770
聪明反被聪明误
you end up getting too clever for your own good.

42:50.470 --> 42:51.120
晚安
Good night.

43:16.320 --> 43:18.590
你自己都不清楚会面对什么
You've no idea what you're in for.
